# ESP32 Firmware Files

This directory will contain Arduino sketches for the smart foot insole microcontroller.

## Files to be created:

- `main.ino` - Main firmware entry point
- `sensors.h` - Sensor initialization & reading
- `wifi_config.h` - WiFi & HTTPS setup
- `api_client.h` - Backend API communication
- `anomaly_detection.h` - Local edge computing
- `OTA_update.h` - Over-the-Air update mechanism

## Placeholder for future development.

See parent directory README.md for specifications.
